about.me: SkyLightPool has been operational since ITN. We strives to give back to its stakeholders through in-depth research and analysis of Cardano and its ecosystem. We are working on making these functionalities available soon.
about.server: Our network architecture includes a dedicated high-end bare-metal server (32 cores, 128GB, 1Gbps Network) and a number of geographically distributed cloud servers. We actively monitor our network and constantly improve upon our infrastructure/tooling.
